{"id":17934,"date":"2022-12-31T04:19:32","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:19:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:19:32","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:19:32","slug":"kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe-2\/","title":{"rendered":"Kia Seltos 2024 t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, th\u00eam c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>M\u1eabu xe g\u1ea7m cao c\u1ee1 nh\u1ecf tinh ch\u1ec9nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1, b\u1ed5 sung trang b\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">So v\u1edbi phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u0169, Seltos m\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t m\u0169i h\u1ed5 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n, th\u00eam c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e8n LED.  C\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ed1c h\u00fat gi\u00f3 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e8n s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 LED n\u1eb1m d\u1ecdc.  C\u1ea3n sau h\u1ea7m h\u1ed1 v\u00e0 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp.  \u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf \u0111u\u00f4i xe l\u00e0 c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n h\u1eadu LED m\u1edbi, tr\u1ea3i d\u00e0i h\u1ebft chi\u1ec1u r\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a xe.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Seltos phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n m\u1edbi l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n.  \u1ea2nh: Kia\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe.jpg\" title=\"kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Seltos phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n m\u1edbi l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n.  \u1ea2nh: Kia<\/p>\n<p>  <img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441443_189_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"M\u1eabu SUV c\u1ee1 nh\u1ecf tinh ch\u1ec9nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf.\" title=\"1672441443_189_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441443_69_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"Xe b\u1ed5 sung ba m\u00e0u ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t m\u1edbi, tinh ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1, t\u0103ng c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t.\" title=\"1672441443_69_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441444_138_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"L\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t m\u0169i h\u1ed5 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n, b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u00e8n LED trang tr\u00ed.\" title=\"1672441444_138_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441444_782_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"H\u1ecda ti\u1ebft b\u1ed9 v\u00e0nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u1ea1i.\" title=\"1672441444_782_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441444_20_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"C\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n h\u1eadu m\u1edbi, n\u1ed1i li\u1ec1n nhau bao tr\u1ecdn chi\u1ec1u r\u1ed9ng xe.\" title=\"1672441444_20_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441444_411_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"C\u1ea3n sau h\u1ea7m h\u1ed1 h\u01a1n.\" title=\"1672441444_411_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441444_950_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t tinh ch\u1ec9nh.\" title=\"1672441444_950_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441444_408_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"C\u1eb7p m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh 10,25 inch, m\u1ed9t cho b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cho h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed.\" title=\"1672441444_408_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441444_178_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"B\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 10,25 inch sau v\u00f4-l\u0103ng.\" title=\"1672441444_178_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441444_910_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"Khoang h\u00e0nh l\u00fd r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i.\" title=\"1672441444_910_kia-seltos-2024-tang-suc-manh-them-cong-nghe\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean, Seltos 2024 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 v\u00e0nh m\u1edbi v\u00e0 th\u00eam c\u00e1c t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u s\u1eafc m\u1edbi, nh\u01b0 xanh Pluton, \u0111en Fusion, xanh Valais.  Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1eabu X-Line m\u1edbi v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t \u0111en m\u1edd, c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n m\u00e0u \u0111en b\u00f3ng, gi\u00e1 n\u00f3c v\u00e0 b\u1ed9 v\u00e0nh 18 inch.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Seltos 2023 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u1ea1i, t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n trung t\u00e2m v\u1edbi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh 4,2 inch v\u00e0 c\u00e1c n\u00fat tinh ch\u1ec9nh.  \u0110\u1eb1ng sau v\u00f4-l\u0103ng l\u00e0 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 10,25 inch v\u00e0 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng 10,25 inch cho h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng th\u00f4ng tin gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed.  C\u00e1c l\u1ed7 th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u1ea1i.  H\u00e3ng xe H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn c\u1ed1p \u0111i\u1ec7n, h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m m\u00e1t, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt OTA v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a s\u1ed1.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u0110\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 2.0 quen thu\u1ed9c cho c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 146 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c, m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i 180 Nm.  H\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 bi\u1ebfn thi\u00ean li\u00ean t\u1ee5c iVT, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng 4 b\u00e1nh.  \u0110\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 t\u0103ng \u00e1p 1.6 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh ch\u1ec9nh t\u0103ng c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t th\u00eam 20 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c l\u00ean 195 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c.  H\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 ly h\u1ee3p k\u00e9p 8 c\u1ea5p m\u1edbi thay cho 7 c\u1ea5p.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u1ede phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n 2024, Seltos \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i nh\u01b0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u00e1nh va ch\u1ea1m ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi t\u00ednh n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i xe \u0111\u1ea1p, c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00f9, gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9.  Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u1eabu SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e8n pha, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1eef l\u00e0n v\u00e0 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh quan s\u00e1t ph\u00eda sau.  B\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p c\u00f3 th\u00eam h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh th\u00f4ng minh, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e1i xe tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cao t\u1ed1c, c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n c\u1eaft ngang khi l\u00f9i.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Kia Seltos s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n ra th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng M\u1ef9 v\u00e0o n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2023 v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u00e0o g\u1ea7n th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">Minh V\u0169 (theo Carscoops)<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>M\u1eabu xe g\u1ea7m cao c\u1ee1 nh\u1ecf tinh ch\u1ec9nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1, b\u1ed5 sung trang b\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng. So v\u1edbi phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u0169, Seltos m\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t m\u0169i h\u1ed5 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n, th\u00eam c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e8n LED. C\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ed1c h\u00fat gi\u00f3 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":16198,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\